      "text": "Configure the files in directory \"/etc/audit/rules.d/\" and the \"/etc/audit/auditd.conf\" file to have a mode of \"0640\" with the following commands:\n\n$ sudo chmod 0640 /etc/audit/rules.d/audit.rules\n$ sudo chmod 0640 /etc/audit/rules.d/[customrulesfile].rules\n$ sudo chmod 0640 /etc/audit/auditd.conf",
